snippet.title: Headquarters: World War II Dev Log #11
snippet.description:
In this new Dev Log, we want to tell you more about how we approach the design of Skirmish and Multiplayer modes in Headquarters: World War II. The Dev will explain our thinking process and highlight key decisions on the way from the first drafts to the final implementation.  
Check out the full article here: https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1840800?emclan=103582791471167652&emgid=4133813065579231441
